      "title": "Set the function output",
      "content": "The condition $f(x)=4$ gives this equation.\n$$4=\\frac{10}{7}x+\\frac{8}{7}$$"
    },
    {
      "title": "Clear the denominators",
      "content": "Multiply both sides by $7$.\n$$28=10x+8$$"
    },
    {
      "title": "Isolate the variable",
      "content": "Subtract $8$, then divide by $10$.\n$$20=10x$$\n$$x=2$$\nThe answer is <strong>2</strong>."
